(45, 'Vì sao ngân hàng không mua vàng từ người dân?', '<?xml encoding=\"utf-8\" ?><div class=\"article__sapo cms-desc\" style=\'font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 1.2rem; color: rgb(59, 61, 63); font-family: arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, \"Helvetica Neue\", Arial, sans-serif, \"Apple Color Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Symbol\", \"Noto Color Emoji\";\'>TPO - 4 ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng qu&#7889;c doanh s&#7869; b&aacute;n v&agrave;ng mi&#7871;ng SJC t&#7915; chi&#7873;u mai (3/6) nh&#432;ng s&#7869; ch&#7881; b&aacute;n m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng mua l&#7841;i khi ng&#432;&#7901;i d&acirc;n c&oacute; nhu c&#7847;u b&aacute;n ra ho&#7863;c ch&#7889;t l&#7901;i. C&aacute;c ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng kh&#7859;ng &#273;&#7883;nh, vi&#7879;c b&aacute;n v&agrave;ng &#273;&#7875; t&#259;ng cung v&agrave; gi&#7843;m ch&ecirc;nh l&#7879;ch v&#7899;i gi&aacute; th&#7871; gi&#7899;i ch&#7913; kh&ocirc;ng kinh doanh &#273;&#7875; h&#432;&#7903;ng l&#7907;i nhu&#7853;n.</div><p style=\'font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(52, 58, 64); font-family: arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, \"Helvetica Neue\", Arial, sans-serif, \"Apple Color Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Symbol\", \"Noto Color Emoji\";\'></p><p style=\"margin: 1.6rem auto 0px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; margin: 1.6rem auto 0px;\">M&#7909;c ti&ecirc;u&nbsp;<a href=\"https://tienphong.vn/tag/b%c3%acnh+%e1%bb%95n.tpo\" title=\"b&igrave;nh &#7893;n\" style=\"color: rgb(165, 10, 2); transition: all 0.1s ease-in-out 0s;\">b&igrave;nh &#7893;n</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://tienphong.vn/tag/th%e1%bb%8b+tr%c6%b0%e1%bb%9dng.tpo\" title=\"th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng\" style=\"color: rgb(165, 10, 2); transition: all 0.1s ease-in-out 0s;\">th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng</a></span></p><p style=\"margin: 1.6rem auto 0px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"text-size-adjust: 100%;\">B&#7889;n&nbsp;</span><a href=\"htt