;t &#273;&#7897;ng cung &#7913;ng c&#7847;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c hi&#7875;u l&agrave; ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng can thi&#7879;p m&#7897;t chi&#7873;u &#273;&#7875; b&igrave;nh &#7893;n gi&aacute; v&agrave;ng tr&ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng.</p><p style=\'margin: 1.6rem auto 0px; color: rgb(52, 58, 64); font-family: arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, \"Helvetica Neue\", Arial, sans-serif, \"Apple Color Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Symbol\", \"Noto Color Emoji\"; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\'>\"C&#7847;n hi&#7875;u r&otilde; r&#7857;ng nh&#7919;ng &#273;&#7883;a &#273;i&#7875;m b&aacute;n&nbsp;<a href=\"https://tienphong.vn/nguoi-mua-vang-lo-nang-post1642476.tpo\" style=\"color: rgb(165, 10, 2); transition: all 0.1s ease-in-out 0s;\">v&agrave;ng mi&#7871;ng SJC</a>&nbsp;t&#7841;i Agribank n&oacute;i ri&ecirc;ng v&agrave; c&#7911;a b&#7889;n ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i nh&agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c n&oacute;i chung ch&#7881; l&agrave; &#273;i&#7875;m cung &#7913;ng v&agrave;ng mi&#7871;ng, ch&#7913; kh&ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i &#273;&#7883;a &#273;i&#7875;m kinh doanh mua - b&aacute;n v&agrave;ng mi&#7871;ng\", b&agrave; Ph&#432;&#7907;ng nh&#7845;n m&#7841;nh.</p><p style=\'margin: 1.6rem auto 0px; color: rgb(52, 58, 64); font-family: arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, \"Helvetica Neue\", Arial, sans-serif, \"Apple Color Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Symbol\", \"Noto Color Emoji\"; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\'>&#272;&#7841;i di&#7879;n m&#7897;t ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng qu&#7889;c doanh cho hay, h&#7885; d&#7921; ki&#7871;n b&aacute;n ra th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng theo m&#7913;c gi&aacute; n&#7857;m trong bi&ecirc;n &#273;&#7897; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c Ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng Nh&agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c cho ph&eacute;p.</p><p style=\'margin: 1.6rem auto 0px; color: rgb(52, 58, 64); font-family: arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, \"Helvetica Neue\", Arial, sans-serif, \"Apple Color Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Symbol\", \"Noto Color Emoji\"; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\'>C&aacute;c nh&agrave; b&#259;ng qu&#7889;c doanh kh&#7859;ng &#273;&#7883;nh vi&#7879;c b&aacute;n v&agrave;ng nh&#7857;m th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n m&#7909;c ti&ecirc;u \"b&igrave;nh &#7893;n\" th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng theo ch&#7911; tr&#432;&#417;ng c&#7911;a Ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng Nh&agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c, kh&ocirc;ng v&igrave; m&#7909;c ti&ecirc;u l&#7907;i nhu&#7853;n.</p><p style=\'margin: 1.6rem auto 0px; color: rgb(52, 58, 64); font-family: arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, \"Helvetica Neue\", Arial, sans-serif, \"Apple Color Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Symbol\", \"Noto Color Emoji\"; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\'>Chuy&ecirc;n gia t&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh Nguy&#7877;n &#272;&#7913;c H&ugrave;ng Linh cho hay, Ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng Nh&agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c b&aacute;n v&agrave;ng b&igrave;nh &#7893;n th&ocirc;ng qua 4 ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng qu&#7889;c doanh &#273;&#7875; t&#259;ng cung, gi&#7843;m ch&ecirc;nh l&#7879;ch gi&aacute; b&aacute;n trong n&#432;&#7899;c v&agrave; th&#7871; gi&#7899;i. M&#7909;c &#273;&iacute;ch ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; b&aacute;n, kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; m&#7909;c &#273;&iacute;ch mua l&#7841;i.</p><p style=\'margin: 1.6rem auto 0px; color: rgb(52, 58, 64); font-family: arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, \"Helvetica Neue\", Arial, sans-serif, \"Apple Color Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Symbol\", \"Noto Color Emoji\"; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\'>&ldquo;Ai c&oacute; nhu c&#7847;u mua ch&iacute;nh &#273;&aacute;ng nh&#432; t&iacute;ch tr&#7919;, cho t&#7863;ng c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#7871;n c&aacute;c ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i nh&agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7881; &#273;&#7883;nh &#273;&#7875; mua, c&oacute; th&#7875; mua &#273;&#432;&#7907;c gi&aacute; t&#7889;t h&#417;n gi&aacute; b&aacute;n &#7903; c&#7917;a h&agrave;ng ngo&agrave;i. Khi gi&aacute; b&aacute;n t&#7915; ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng th&#7845;p h&#417;n, th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng t&#7921; ph&#7843;i gi&#7843;m gi&aacute;. Gi&#7843;m gi&aacute; ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; b&igrave;nh &#7893;n, m&#7909;c &#273;&iacute;ch k&eacute;o gi&#7843;m ch&ecirc;nh l&#7879;ch coi nh&#432; &#273;&#7841;t&rdquo;, &ocirc;ng Linh n&oacute;i.</p><p style=\'margin: 1.6rem auto 0px; color: rgb(52, 58, 64); font-family: arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, \"Helvetica Neue\", Arial, sans-serif, \"Apple Color Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Symbol\", \"Noto Color Emoji\"; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\'>&Ocirc;ng Linh cho bi&#7871;t c&aacute;c ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i nh&agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng mua, ng&#432;&#7901;i d&acirc;n c&oacute; th&#7875; b&aacute;n cho nh&#7919;ng ai mu&#7889;n mua ho&#7863;c cho c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng ty v&agrave; c&#7917;a h&agrave;ng v&agrave;ng th&ocirc;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng. V&agrave;ng mi&#7871;ng SJC c&oacute; l&#7907;i th&#7871; l&agrave; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o b&#7903;i th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u v&agrave; ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng, c&oacute; thanh kho&#7843;n t&#7889;t nh&#7845;t th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng.</p><p style=\'margin: 1.6rem auto 0px; color: rgb(52, 58, 64); font-family: arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, \"Helvetica Neue\", Arial, sans-serif, \"Apple Color Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Symbol\", \"Noto Color Emoji\"; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\'><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; margin: 1.6rem auto 0px;\">Sau 3 ng&agrave;y, gi&aacute; v&agrave;ng mi&#7871;ng gi&#7843;m g&#7847;n 8 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/l&#432;&#7907;ng</span></p><p style=\'margin: 1.6rem auto 0px; color: rgb(52, 58, 64); font-family: arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSyste