, \"Segoe UI Symbol\", \"Noto Color Emoji\"; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\'>&#272;&agrave; gi&#7843;m m&#7841;nh c&#7911;a gi&aacute; v&agrave;ng mi&#7871;ng khi Ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng Nh&agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c thay &#273;&#7893;i c&aacute;ch b&igrave;nh &#7893;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng.</p><p style=\'margin: 1.6rem auto 0px; color: rgb(52, 58, 64); font-family: arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, \"Helvetica Neue\", Arial, sans-serif, \"Apple Color Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Symbol\", \"Noto Color Emoji\"; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\'>C&#417; quan qu&#7843;n l&yacute; tr&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&oacute; &#273;&atilde; t&#7893; ch&#7913;c&nbsp;<a href=\"https://tienphong.vn/nguoi-mua-vang-lo-nang-post1642476.tpo\" style=\"color: rgb(165, 10, 2); transition: all 0.1s ease-in-out 0s;\">&#273;&#7845;u th&#7847;u&nbsp;</a>&#273;&#7875; t&#259;ng cung v&agrave;ng mi&#7871;ng, nh&#7857;m h&#7841; ch&ecirc;nh l&#7879;ch gi&aacute; so v&#7899;i th&#7871; gi&#7899;i. Sau 9 phi&ecirc;n &#273;&#7845;u th&#7847;u, Ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng Nh&agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c cung &#7913;ng ra th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng 48.500 l&#432;&#7907;ng v&agrave;ng SJC, t&#432;&#417;ng &#273;&#432;&#417;ng h&#417;n 1,8 t&#7845;n v&agrave;ng.</p><p style=\'margin: 1.6rem auto 0px; color: rgb(52, 58, 64); font-family: arial, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, \"Helvetica Neue\", Arial, sans-serif, \"Apple Color Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Symbol\", \"Noto Color Emoji\"; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\'>Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, sau m&#7897;t th&aacute;ng &#273;&#7845;u th&#7847;u, m&#7909;c ti&ecirc;u \"h&#7841; nhi&#7879;t\" gi&aacute; v&agrave;ng mi&#7871;ng ch&#432;a &#273;&#7841;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c. Ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng Nh&agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c sau &#273;&oacute; ph&#7843;i d&#7915;ng &#273;&#7845;u th&#7847;u, chuy&#7875;n sang ph&#432;&#417;ng ph&aacute;p b&aacute;n v&agrave;ng tr&#7921;c ti&#787