&#417;ng Trinh hi&#7879;n g&acirc;y nhi&#7873;u tranh c&atilde;i tr&ecirc;n m&#7841;ng x&atilde; h&#7897;i.</h2><p style=\'box-sizing: inherit; margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1.8em; line-height: 1.6; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; content-visibility: auto; opacity: 0.8; color: rgb(29, 35, 46); font-family: \"Noto Serif\", serif !important;\'><img src=\"http://localhost/biznews_rebuild/public/uploads/image/1717312885-665c1d7530590.jpeg\" style=\"width: 1074.29px; height: 748.92px;\" data-filename=\"x6m84z1ggo1-8pkb3rydvn2-tcg64w9bj13.jpg.jpeg\"></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.6; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word; position: relative;\">M&#7899;i &#273;&acirc;y, &#273;&#7841;i di&#7879;n S&#7903; TT&amp;TT TPHCM cho bi&#7871;t &#273;&atilde; n&#7855;m th&ocirc;ng tin v&#7873; nh&#7919;ng ph&aacute;t ng&ocirc;n c&#7911;a Angela Ph&#432;&#417;ng Trinh v&agrave; s&#7869; x&aacute;c minh, ph&#7843;n h&#7891;i sau. &#272;&#7841;i di&#7879;n S&#7903; VH-TT TPHCM cho bi&#7871;t s&#7869; trao &#273;&#7893;i v&#7899;i S&#7903; TT&amp;TT th&ecirc;m v&#7873; tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p c&#7911;a n&#7919; di&#7877;n vi&ecirc;n 9X tr&ecirc;n g&oacute;c &#273;&#7897; chuy&ecirc;n m&ocirc;n v&#259;n h&oacute;a.&nbsp;</p><div id=\"pc-inarticle\" class=\"mt-4 text-center\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></div><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.6; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word; position: relative;\">Hi&#7879;n, b&agrave;i &#273;&#259;ng c&#7911;a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.saostar.vn/tag/angela-phuong-trinh/\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Angela Ph&#432;&#417;ng Trinh</a>&nbsp;nh&#7853;n v&#7873; nhi&#7873;u l&#432;&#7907;t &ldquo;ph&#7851;n n&#7897;&rdquo; c&#7911;a c&#7897;ng &#273;&#7891;ng m&#7841;ng. Tr&#432;&#7899;c l&agrave;n s&oacute;ng b&#7883; ch&#7881; tr&iacute;ch, n&#7919; di&#7877;n vi&ecirc;n h&#7841;n ch&#7871; t&#432;&#417;ng t&aacute;c &#7903; ph&#7847;n b&igrave;nh lu&#7853;n c&#7911;a m&#7895;i b&agrave;i &#273;&#259;ng.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.6; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word; position: relative;\">G&#7847;n &#273;&acirc;y, Angela Ph&#432;&#417;ng Trinh kh&ocirc;ng ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng ngh&#7879; thu&#7853;t s&ocirc;i n&#7893;i nh&#432; tr&#432;&#7899;c. Thay v&agrave;o &#273;&oacute;, t&ecirc;n tu&#7893;i c&#7911;a c&ocirc; th&#432;&#7901;ng xuy&ecirc;n g&#7855;n li&#7873;n v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng b&agrave;i &#273;&#259;ng thi&#7871;u ki&#7875;m ch&#7913;ng khoa h&#7885;c ho&#7863;c nh&#7919;ng chia s&#7867; g&acirc;y tranh c&atilde;i tr&ecirc;n m&#7841;ng x&atilde; h&#7897;i.&nbsp;</p><div id=\"pc-inarticle-2\" class=\"mt-4 text-center\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></div><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.6; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word; position: relative;\">&#272;i&#7875;n h&igrave;nh, th&aacute;ng 8/2021, c&ocirc; &#273;&#259;ng t&#7843;i chuy&#7879;n Nh&acirc;n qu&#7843; b&#7867; ch&acirc;n nh&aacute;i k&egrave;m h&igrave;nh &#7843;nh c&#7911;a m&#7897;t &#273;&#7913;a b&eacute; b&#7883; khuy&#7871;t t&#7853;t. Th&aacute;ng 10/2021, Angela Ph&#432;&#417;ng Trinh t&#7915;ng b&#7883; ph&#7841;t 7,5 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng v&igrave; h&agrave;nh vi cung c&#7845;p th&ocirc;ng tin sai s&#7921; th&#7853;t l&agrave; ch&#7919;a tr&#7883; b&#7879;nh b&#7857;ng giun &#273;&#7845;t.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.6; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word; position: relative;\">Angela Ph&#432;&#417;ng Trinh t&ecirc;n th&#7853;t l&agrave; L&ecirc; Ng&#7885;c Ph&#432;&#417;ng Trinh, sinh n&#259;m 1995. C&ocirc; t&#7915;ng &#273;&oacute;ng phim t&#7915; n&#259;m 7 tu&#7893;i khi &#273;&#7843;m nh&#7853;n m&#7897;t vai trong K&iacute;nh V&#7841;n Hoa. N&#259;m 2005, c&ocirc; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c m&#7897;t &#273;&#7841;o di&#7877;n H&agrave;n Qu&#7889;c l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n v&agrave;o vai nh&acirc;n v&#7853;t Vy l&uacute;c nh&#7887; trong phim M&ugrave;i Ng&ograve; Gai. Sau n&agrave;y, n&#7919; di&#7877;n vi&ecirc;n &iacute;t ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng ngh&#7879; thu&#7853;t nh&#432;ng t&ecirc;n tu&#7893;i v&#7851;n g&acirc;y ch&uacute; &yacute; v&igrave; nhi&#7873;u l&#7847;n ph&aacute;t ng&ocirc;n g&acirc;y tranh c&atilde;i tr&ecirc;n m&#7841;ng x&atilde; h&#7897;i.</p>\n', 13, 33, '1717312885.jpeg', '2024-06-02 07:21:25', '2024-06-02 07:21:25');
