(47, 'Liệu ông Trump có thể trở thành tổng thống Mỹ sau khi bị kết án?', '<?xml encoding=\"utf-8\" ?><h2 class=\"sapo\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; font-family: Roboto; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(54, 54, 54);\">Ch&#7881; c&ograve;n v&agrave;i th&aacute;ng n&#7919;a l&agrave; di&#7877;n ra cu&#7897;c b&#7847;u c&#7917; t&#7893;ng th&#7889;ng M&#7929;, nh&#432;ng Donald Trump l&#7841;i &#273;ang \"b&#7853;n l&#7883;ch tr&igrave;nh &#7903; t&ograve;a &aacute;n\". Cho d&ugrave; nh&#7919;ng c&aacute;o bu&#7897;c nh&#7857;m v&agrave;o &ocirc;ng c&oacute; k&#7871;t th&uacute;c th&#7871; n&agrave;o &#273;i ch&#259;ng n&#7919;a, &ocirc;ng Trump v&#7851;n c&oacute; th&#7875; tranh c&#7917; t&#7893;ng th&#7889;ng.</h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; font-family: Roboto; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(54, 54, 54);\"><img src=\"http://localhost/biznews_rebuild/public/uploads/image/1717313288-665c1f0825811.jpeg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-filename=\"capture (1).jpeg\"></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.6em; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Theo &#272;&agrave;i ph&aacute;t thanh Qu&#7889;c t&#7871; &#272;&#7913;c Deutsche Welle (DW), m&#7897;t c&#7921;u t&#7893;ng th&#7889;ng b&#7883; k&#7871;t &aacute;n trong m&#7897;t phi&ecirc;n t&ograve;a h&igrave;nh s&#7921; l&agrave; tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p &#273;&#7847;u ti&ecirc;n trong l&#7883;ch s&#7917; M&#7929;. V&#7853;y &#273;i&#7873;u n&agrave;y s&#7869; &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng th&#7871; n&agrave;o &#273;&#7871;n vi&#7879;c tranh c&#7917; t&#7893;ng th&#7889;ng c&#7911;a Donald Trump?</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.6em; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Donald Trump, &#7913;ng c&#7917; vi&ecirc;n h&agrave;ng &#273;&#7847;u c&#7911;a &#272;&#7843;ng C&#7897;ng h&ograve;a cho cu&#7897;c b&#7847;u c&#7917; t&#7893;ng th&#7889;ng M&#7929; v&agrave;o th&aacute;ng 11/2024, kh&ocirc;ng c&ograve;n &ldquo;xa l&#7841;&rdquo; v&#7899;i ph&ograve;ng x&#7917; &aacute;n. &#272;&#7847;u n&#259;m nay, b&#7891;i th&#7849;m &#273;o&agrave;n &#7903; New York &#273;&atilde; ra ph&aacute;n quy&#7871;t r&#7857;ng &ocirc;ng s&#7869; ph&#7843;i b&#7891;i th&#432;&#7901;ng thi&#7879;t h&#7841;i h&agrave;ng tri&#7879;u &#273;&ocirc; la cho nh&agrave; v&#259;n E. Jean Carroll v&igrave; t&#7897;i l&#7841;m d&#7909;ng t&igrave;nh d&#7909;c v&agrave; sau &#273;&oacute; l&agrave; ph&#7881; b&aacute;ng, m&#7897;t quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh m&agrave; &ocirc;ng Trump &#273;ang kh&aacute;ng c&aacute;o. &#272;&oacute; l&agrave; m&#7897;t v&#7909; &aacute;n d&acirc;n s&#7921;.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.6em; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Gi&#7901; &#273;&acirc;y, &ocirc;ng Trump &#273;&atilde; tr&#7903; th&agrave;nh c&#7921;u t&#7893;ng th&#7889;ng M&#7929; &#273;&#7847;u ti&ecirc;n b&#7883; k&#7871;t t&#7897;i h&igrave;nh s&#7921; li&ecirc;n quan &#273;&#7871;n v&#7909; chi ti&#7873;n b&#7883;t mi&#7879;ng sao khi&ecirc;u d&acirc;m Stormy Daniels t&#7841;i chi&#7871;n d&#7883;ch tranh c&#7917; n&#259;m 2016.&nbsp;B&#7891;i th&#7849;m &#273;o&agrave;n trong v&#7909; &aacute;n h&igrave;nh s&#7921; x&eacute;t x&#7917; c&#7921;u T&#7893;ng th&#7889;ng M&#7929; Donald Trump v&#7899;i c&aacute;o bu&#7897;c &ldquo;chi ti&#7873;n b&#7883;t mi&#7879;ng&rdquo; &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#432;a ra ph&aacute;n quy&#7871;t v&agrave;o cu&#7889;i gi&#7901; chi&#7873;u ng&agrave;y 30/5, sau ch&#432;a &#273;&#7847;y 12 gi&#7901; ngh&#7883; &aacute;n.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.6em; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Th&#7849;m ph&aacute;n Juan Merchan &#273;&atilde; b&aacute;c b&#7887; y&ecirc;u c&#78