, ph&iacute;a tr&#432;&#7899;c) t&#7841;i phi&ecirc;n x&eacute;t x&#7917; c&#7911;a T&ograve;a &aacute;n T&#7889;i cao Manhattan &#7903; New York, ng&agrave;y 30/5/2024. &#7842;nh: AFP/TTXVN</span><strong><br></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.6em; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>&Ocirc;ng Trump c&oacute; th&#7875; b&#7887; phi&#7871;u trong cu&#7897;c b&#7847;u c&#7917; M&#7929;?&nbsp;</strong></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.6em; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&#272;i&#7873;u n&agrave;y l&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng th&#7875;: &Ocirc;ng Trump &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; b&#7887; phi&#7871;u &#7903; Florida, n&#417;i nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i b&#7883; k&#7871;t &aacute;n s&#7869; b&#7883; t&#432;&#7899;c quy&#7873;n b&#7847;u c&#7917;.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.6em; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Ph&oacute;ng vi&ecirc;n ch&iacute;nh tr&#7883; Maggie Astor vi&#7871;t tr&ecirc;n t&#7901; The New York Times: &ldquo;H&#7847;u h&#7871;t nh&#7919;ng &#273;&#7889;i t&#432;&#7907;ng ph&#7841;m t&#7897;i &#7903; Florida &#273;&#7873;u ch&#7881; c&oacute; quy&#7873;n b&#7847;u c&#7917; sau khi m&atilde;n h&#7841;n t&ugrave; &#273;&#7847;y &#273;&#7911;, bao g&#7891;m c&#7843; vi&#7879;c t&#7841;m tha ho&#7863;c qu&#7843;n ch&#7871; c&#361;ng nh&#432; tr&#7843; t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c kho&#7843;n ti&#7873;n ph&#7841;t v&agrave; l&#7879; ph&iacute;&rdquo;.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.6em; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Nh&#432;ng vi&#7879;c t&#7841;m tha &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i c&#7921;u T&#7893;ng th&#7889;ng Trump c&oacute; th&#7875; s&#7869; kh&ocirc;ng k&#7883;p &#273;&#7875; &ocirc;ng c&oacute; l&#7841;i quy&#7873;n b&#7847;u c&#7917;. V&igrave; v&#7853;y, n&#7871;u b&#7883; k&#7871;t t&#7897;i, &ocirc;ng Trump v&#7851;n c&oacute; th&#7875; tranh c&#7917; t&#7893;ng th&#7889;ng nh&#432;ng kh&ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c b&#7887; phi&#7871;u cho ch&iacute;nh m&igrave;nh.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.6em; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Nh&#432;ng chuy&#7879;n g&igrave; s&#7869; x&#7843;y ra n&#7871;u &ocirc;ng Trump th&#7921;c s&#7921; ph&#7843;i v&agrave;o t&ugrave;?&nbsp;Hi&#7879;n kh&ocirc;ng ai bi&#7871;t s&#7869; nh&#432; th&#7871; n&agrave;o trong tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p n&agrave;y.&nbsp;Erwin Chemerinsky, chuy&ecirc;n gia lu&#7853;t t&#7841;i &#272;&#7841;i h&#7885;c California-Berkeley, n&oacute;i v&#7899;i t&#7901; New York Times: &ldquo;Cho &#273;&#7871;n nay, ch&uacute;ng ta ch&#432;a t&#7915;ng ch&#7913;ng ki&#7871;n &#273;i&#7873;u n&agrave;y x&#7843;y ra. T&#7845;t c&#7843; ch&#7881; l&agrave; suy &#273;o&aacute;n&rdquo;.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.6em; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">V&#7873; m&#7863;t ph&aacute;p l&yacute;, &ocirc;ng Trump v&#7851;n &#273;&#7911; &#273;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n tranh c&#7917;, ngay c&#7843; khi \"&#273;&#7913;ng sau song s&#7855;t\". Nh&#432;ng t&#7845;t nhi&ecirc;n m&#7897;t t&#7893;ng th&#7889;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c b&#7847;u khi &#273;ang &#7903; trong t&ugrave; s&#7869; &#273;&#7863;t ra m&#7897;t th&aacute;ch th&#7913;c v&#7873; m&#7863;t h&#7853;u c&#7847;n. Nh&agrave; b&aacute;o Astor suy &#273;o&aacute;n r&#7857;ng \"&ocirc;ng Trump c&oacute; th&#7875; ki&#7879;n &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c tr&#7843; t&#7921; do tr&ecirc;n c&#417; s&#7903; r&#7857;ng vi&#7879;c b&#7887; t&ugrave; &#273;ang ng&#259;n c&#7843;n &ocirc;ng th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n ngh&#297;a v&#7909; hi&#7871;n ph&aacute;p v&#7899;i t&#432; c&aacute;ch l&agrave; t&#7893;ng th&#7889;ng\".&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.6em; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Nh&#432;ng v&igrave; ch&#432;a t&#7915;ng c&oacute; ti&#7873;n l&#7879; trong l&#7883;ch s&#7917; M&#7929; n&ecirc;n kh&ocirc;ng th&#7875; n&oacute;i tr&#432;&#7899;c m&#7885;i chuy&#7879;n s&#7869; di&#7877;n ra nh&#432; th&#7871; n&agrave;o.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.6em; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">N&#7871;u &#273;&#7855;c c&#7917;, li&#7879;u Trump c&oacute; th&#7875; b&aacute;c b&#7887; c&aacute;c v&#7909; ki&#7879;n ch&#7889;ng l&#7841;i &ocirc;ng hay t&#7921; &acirc;n x&aacute; cho ch&iacute;nh m&igrave;nh?&nbsp;V&#7873; l&yacute; thuy&#7871;t, &ocirc;ng Trump c&oacute; th&#7875; gi&#7843;m &aacute;n t&ugrave; hay hu&#7927; b&#7843;n &aacute;n, ho&#7863;c th&#7853;m ch&iacute; t&igrave;m c&aacute;ch t&#7921; &acirc;n x&aacute; ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n cho b&#7843;n th&acirc;n, nh&#432;ng &#273;&acirc;y s&#7869; l&agrave; nh&#7919;ng t&iacute;n hi&#7879;u c&#7921;c &#273;oan v&#7873; quy&#7873;n l&#7921;c c&#7911;a t&#7893;ng th&#7889;ng v&agrave; c&oacute; th&#7875; s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#432;a ra tr&#432;&#7899;c T&ograve;a &aacute;n T&#7889;i cao &#273;&#7875; xem x&eacute;t v&#7873; t&iacute;nh h&#7907;p hi&#7871;n c&#7911;a ch&uacute;ng.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.6em; font-family: Arial; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Ngo&agrave;i ra, T&#7893;ng th&#7889;ng Joe Biden c&oacute; th&#7875; &acirc;n x&aacute; cho &ocirc;ng Trump. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, nh&#7919;ng h&agrave;nh &#273;&#7897;ng nh&#432; v&#7853;y s&#7869; ch&#7881; &aacute;p d&#7909;ng cho c&aacute;c v&#7909; &aacute;n li&ecirc;n bang c&#7911;a &ocirc;ng Trump, ch&#7913; kh&ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i v&#7909; x&eacute;t x&#7917; t&#7897;i chi ti&#7873;n b&#7883;t mi&#7879;ng c&#7911;a bang New York, c&#361;ng nh&#432; v&#7909; can thi&#7879;p b&#7847;u c&#7917; &#7903; Georgia, v&igrave; c&aacute;c t&#7893;ng th&#7889;ng kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; quy&#7873;n &acirc;n x&aacute; cho c&aacute;c b&#7843;n &aacute;n &#7903; c&#7845;p bang.</p>\n', 13, 35, '1717313288.jpeg', '2024-06-02 07:28:08', '2024-06-02 07:28:08'),
