(49, 'Ngành Công nghệ Ô tô số: mới những đầy \"ma lực\"!!!', '<?xml encoding=\"utf-8\" ?><?xml encoding=\"utf-8\" ?><?xml encoding=\"utf-8\" ?><?xml encoding=\"utf-8\" ?><?xml encoding=\"utf-8\" ?><?xml encoding=\"utf-8\" ?><h2 class=\"detail-sapo\" data-role=\"sapo\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: Inter; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 26px;\">C&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; &Ocirc; t&ocirc; s&#7889; (ASE &ndash; Automotive Software Engineering) l&agrave; ng&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; m&#7899;i n&#7893;i c&oacute; t&#7889;c &#273;&#7897; ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n nhanh ch&oacute;ng, li&ecirc;n quan &#273;&#7871;n vi&#7879;c ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n, t&iacute;ch h&#7907;p ph&#7847;n m&#7873;m cho &ocirc; t&ocirc;.</h2><div class=\"detail-cmain\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Inter; font-size: 14px;\"><div class=\"detail-content afcbc-body\" data-role=\"content\" style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; max-width: 100%; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 15px;\"><h2 style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; line-height: 33.6px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 24px !important;\">Ng&agrave;nh C&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; &Ocirc; t&ocirc; s&#7889;: c&#417; h&#7897;i m&#7899;i cho c&aacute;c b&#7841;n tr&#7867;</h2><p style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 28.8px;\">Ng&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p &ocirc; t&ocirc; &#273;ang tr&#7843;i qua giai &#273;o&#7841;n chuy&#7875;n &#273;&#7893;i m&#7841;nh m&#7869; v&#7899;i s&#7921; ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n c&#7911;a c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; s&#7889;. C&aacute;c ph&#432;&#417;ng ti&#7879;n giao th&ocirc;ng ng&agrave;y nay &#273;&#432;&#7907;c trang b&#7883; nhi&#7873;u h&#7879; th&#7889;ng &#273;i&#7879;n t&#7917;, ph&#7847;n m&#7873;m th&ocirc;ng minh, mang &#273;&#7871;n cho ng&#432;&#7901;i d&ugrave;ng nh&#7919;ng tr&#7843;i nghi&#7879;m l&aacute;i xe an to&agrave;n, ti&#7879;n nghi v&agrave; th&uacute; v&#7883; h&#417;n.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 28.8px;\">N&#7855;m b&#7855;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c xu h&#432;&#7899;ng ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n c&#7911;a ng&agrave;nh, Tr&#432;&#7901;ng &#272;&#7841;i h&#7885;c FPT &#273;&atilde; ti&ecirc;n phong &#273;&agrave;o t&#7841;o ng&agrave;nh C&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; &Ocirc; t&ocirc; s&#7889; (ASE) nh&#7857;m &#273;&aacute;p &#7913;ng nhu c&#7847;u ng&agrave;y c&agrave;ng cao v&#7873; ngu&#7891;n nh&acirc;n l&#7921;c ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng cao cho l&#297;nh v&#7921;c n&agrave;y.</p><p style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 28.8px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost/biznews_rebuild/public/uploads/image/1717314397-665c235daac56.jpeg\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-filename=\"screenshot-2024-06-02-124840-1717307325715179908038.png.jpeg\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 28.8px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(72, 72, 72); font-size: 14px; font-style: italic; text-align: center;\">Sinh vi&ecirc;n &#272;&#7841;i h&#7885;c FPT v&#7899;i ng&agrave;nh C&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; &Ocirc; t&ocirc; s&#7889;</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 28.8px;\">Ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh &#273;&agrave;o t&#7841;o chuy&ecirc;n ng&agrave;nh C&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; &Ocirc; t&ocirc; s&#7889; (ASE &ndash; Automotive Software Engineering) t&#7841;i &#272;&#7841;i h&#7885;c FPT &#273;&#432;&#7907;c thi&#7871;t k&#7871; nh&#7857;m &#273;&aacute;p &#7913;ng nhu c&#7847;u nh&acirc;n l&#7921;c thi&#7871;t y&#7871;u trong ng&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p &ocirc; t&ocirc; v&agrave; h&#7879; th&#7889;ng nh&uacute;ng, trong b&#7889;i c&#7843;nh Ph&#7847;n m&#7873;m (software) &#273;&#432;&#7907;c xem l&agrave; nh&acirc;n t&#7889; ch&#7911; &#273;&#7841;o quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh to&agrave;n b&#7897; h&#7879; th&#7889;ng v&agrave; ph&#432;&#417;ng th&#7913;c v&#7853;n h&agrave;nh &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i &ocirc; t&ocirc; (SDV &ndash; Software-Defined Vehicle), &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t trong giai &#273;o&#7841;n ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n m&#7841;nh m&#7869; c&#7911;a xu h&#432;&#7899;ng &ocirc; t&ocirc; t&#7921; l&aacute;i v&agrave; c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; &ocirc; t&ocirc; ti&ecirc;n ti&#7871;n.&nbsp;</p><div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" type=\"boxhighlight\" style=\"display: inline-block; flex-direction: column; margin: 0px auto 15px; position: relative; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; width: 785.259px; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word; cursor: default; max-width: 100%;\"><div class=\"boxhighlight\" data-layout=\"type-1\" data-link=\"https://daihoc.fpt.edu.vn/hoc-nganh-cong-nghe-o-to-so-tai-truong-dh-fpt-mo-ra-canh-cua-den-tuong-lai-2/\" style=\"padding: 10px 15px; background-color: rgb(240, 241, 245); border-left: 3px solid rgb(204, 0, 0); border-radius: 3px;\"><div class=\"boxhighlight-content\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(217, 218, 222); padding-bottom: 15px;\">M&#7897;t s&#7889; &#273;i&#7875;m kh&aacute;c bi&#7879;t c&#7911;a chuy&ecirc;n ng&agrave;nh C&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; &ocirc; t&ocirc; s&#7889; t&#7841;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng &#272;H FPT<br><br>Ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh &#273;&#432;&#7907;c thi&#7871;t k&#7871; tham kh&#7843;o khuy&#7871;n ngh&#7883; c&#7911;a Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i M&aacute;y t&iacute;nh Hoa K&#7923; v&#7873; ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh &#273;&agrave;o t&#7841;o b&#7853;c &#273;&#7841;i h&#7885;c ng&agrave;nh C&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; th&ocirc;ng tin ACM (Association for Computing Machinery), chu&#7849;n ki&#7875;m &#273;&#7883;nh AQAS (The Agency for Quality Assurance through Accreditation of Study Programs), ABET (Accreditation Board for Engineering and Technology) cho ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh &#273;&agrave;o t&#7841;o, s&aacute;ng ki&#7871;n CDIO cho x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng chu&#7849;n &#273;&#7847;u ra (learning outcome) c&#7911;a ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh &#273;&agrave;o t&#7841;o, v&agrave; ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh &#273;&agrave;o t&#7841;o b&#7853;c &#273;&#7841;i h&#7885;c c&aacute;c chuy&ecirc;n ng&agrave;nh v&#7873; h&#7879; th&#7889;ng &ocirc; t&ocirc; v&agrave; &#273;i&#7873;u khi&#7875;n c&#7911;a m&#7897;t s&#7889; tr&#432;&#7901;ng qu&#7889;c t&#7871; v&agrave; trong n&#432;&#7899;c.<br><br>Ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh tham kh&#7843;o &aacute;p d&#7909;ng Ti&ecirc;u chu&#7849;n qu&#7889;c t&#7871; v&#7873; an to&agrave;n ch&#7913;c n&#259;ng trong ng&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t xe c&#417; gi&#7899;i (ISO 26262) c&#361;ng nh&#432; K&#7929; thu&#7853;t an ninh m&#7841;ng ng&agrave;nh &ocirc; t&ocirc; (ISO 21434).<br><br>H&#7885;c ng&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; nh&#432;ng v&#7851;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c trang b&#7883; 2 ngo&#7841;i ng&#7919;: Ngo&agrave;i ti&#7871;ng Anh, sinh vi&ecirc;n kh&#7889;i ng&agrave;nh C&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; th&ocirc;ng tin &#273;&#432;&#7907;c h&#7885;c th&ecirc;m ng&ocirc;n ng&#7919; Nh&#7853;t. C&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; &ocirc; t&ocirc; s&#7889; l&agrave; m&#7897;t ng&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p to&agrave;n c&#7847;u, v&#7899;i s&#7921; tham gia c&#7911;a nhi&#7873;u qu&#7889;c gia tr&ecirc;n th&#7871; gi&#7899;i.<br><br>Sinh vi&ecirc;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c trang b&#7883; c&aacute;c ki&#7871;n th&#7913;c c&#417; b&#7843;n c&#7911;a ng&agrave;nh C&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; th&ocirc;ng tin c&ugrave;ng c&aacute;c ph&#432;&#417;ng ph&aacute;p lu&#7853;n, c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; n&#7873;n t&#7843;ng v&agrave; chuy&ecirc;n s&acirc;u c&#7911;a chuy&ecirc;n ng&agrave;nh C&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; &Ocirc; t&ocirc; s&#7889;, t&#7853;p trung ch&#7911; y&#7871;u v&agrave;o Ki&#7871;n tr&uacute;c ph&#7847;n m&#7873;m &ocirc; t&ocirc; (Autosar), h&#7879; th&#7889;ng nh&uacute;ng (embedded systems), l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh v&agrave; thi&#7871;t k&#7871; h&#7879; th&#7889;ng th&ocirc;ng tin gi&#7843;i tr&iacute; tr&ecirc;n &ocirc; t&ocirc; (IVI).<br><br>V&#7899;i h&#7885;c k&#7923; \"On-the-Job Training\" (OJT) l&agrave; m&#7897;t ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh h&#7885;c t&#7853;p th&#7921;c t&#7871; d&agrave;nh cho sinh vi&ecirc;n tr&#432;&#7901;ng &#272;&#7841;i h&#7885;c FPT, sinh vi&ecirc;n s&#7869; l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c t&#7841;i doanh nghi&#7879;p c&oacute; li&ecirc;n k&#7871;t v&#7899;i nh&agrave; tr&#432;&#7901;ng t&#7915; 4 &ndash; 8. &#272;&acirc;y l&agrave; c&#417; h&#7897;i qu&yacute; gi&aacute; &#273;&#7875; sinh vi&ecirc;n &aacute;p d&#7909;ng ki&#7871;n th&#7913;c v&agrave; k&#7929; n&#259;ng &#273;&atilde; h&#7885;c v&agrave;o th&#7921;c t&#7871;, &#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i t&iacute;ch l&#361;y kinh nghi&#7879;m l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c v&agrave; &#273;&#7883;nh h&#432;&#7899;ng t&#432;&#417;ng lai cho b&#7843;n th&acirc;n.</div><a class=\"boxhighlight-link no-anchor-preview\" href=\"https://daihoc.fpt.edu.vn/hoc-nganh-cong-nghe-o-to-so-tai-truong-dh-fpt-mo-ra-canh-cua-den-tuong-lai-2/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"display: flex; justify-content: flex-end; border-top: 1px solid rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-top: 5px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102) !important;\">https://daihoc.fpt.edu.vn/hoc-nganh-c...</a></div></div><p style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 28.8px;\">Hi&#7879;n nay, nhu c&#7847;u ngu&#7891;n lao &#273;&#7897;ng trong l&#297;nh v&#7921;c c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; &ocirc; t&ocirc; s&#7889; c&#361;ng &#273;ang ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n ng&agrave;y c&agrave;ng cao, c&aacute;c tr&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#7841;i h&#7885;c c&#361;ng n&#7855;m b&#7855;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c xu h&#432;&#7899;ng n&agrave;y &#273;&#7875; c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&agrave;o t&#7841;o, &#273;&aacute;p &#7913;ng nhu c&#7847;u ngu&#7891;n nh&acirc;n l&#7921;c ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng cho l&#297;nh v&#7921;c &#273;&#7847;y h&#7845;p d&#7851;n. C&#7909; th&#7875;, Tr&#432;&#7901;ng &#272;&#7841;i h&#7885;c FPT h&#7907;p t&aacute;c FPT Automotive m&#7903; chuy&ecirc;n ng&agrave;nh C&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; &ocirc; t&ocirc; s&#7889; (ASE &ndash; Automotive Software Engineering).</p><p style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 28.8px;\">V&#7899;i th&#7871; m&#7841;nh 10 n&#259;m ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng trong ng&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p &ocirc; t&ocirc; s&#7889;,&nbsp;FPT c&#361;ng s&#7903; h&#7919;u &#273;&#7897;i ng&#361; h&#417;n 4.000 chuy&ecirc;n gia gi&agrave;u kinh nghi&#7879;m v&#7873; &ocirc;t&ocirc;, h&#7879; th&#7889;ng nh&uacute;ng. &#272;&acirc;y c&#361;ng l&agrave; b&#432;&#7899;c t&#7841;o &#273;&agrave; cho vi&#7879;c k&#7923; v&#7885;ng &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; &#273;&#7849;y m&#7841;nh s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng v&agrave; ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng ngu&#7891;n nh&acirc;n l&#7921;c cho ng&agrave;nh, hi&#7879;n th&#7921;c h&oacute;a chi&#7871;n l&#432;&#7907;c ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n trong t&#432;&#417;ng lai. Vi&#7879;c th&agrave;nh l&#7853;p chuy&ecirc;n ng&agrave;nh &#273;&#7841;i h&#7885;c m&#7899;i t&#7841;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng &#272;&#7841;i h&#7885;c FPT s&#7869; gi&uacute;p sinh vi&ecirc;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c trang b&#7883; ki&#7871;n th&#7913;c v&agrave; k&#7929; n&#259;ng th&#7921;c ti&#7877;n; c&oacute; c&#417; h&#7897;i l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c trong nhi&#7873;u d&#7921; &aacute;n c&#7911;a c&ocirc;ng ty tr&ecirc;n to&agrave;n c&#7847;u sau khi t&#7889;t nghi&#7879;p.</p><p style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 28.8px;\">C&oacute; th&#7875; n&oacute;i, ng&agrave;nh C&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; &Ocirc; t&ocirc; s&#7889; l&agrave; m&#7897;t ng&agrave;nh m&#7899;i. V&#7899;i c&#417; h&#7897;i h&#7885;c t&#7853;p trong l&#297;nh v&#7921;c &Ocirc; t&ocirc; s&#7889; s&#7869; m&#7903; ra m&#7897;t t&#432;&#417;ng lai tri&#7875;n v&#7885;ng cho c&aacute;c b&#7841;n sinh vi&ecirc;n. &#272;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t, trong xu th&#7871; ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n s&#7889; h&oacute;a c&aacute;c ng&agrave;nh ngh&#7873;, trong &#273;&oacute; c&oacute; c&aacute;c ng&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p. B&ecirc;n c&#7841;nh &#273;&oacute;, m&ocirc;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c l&#297;nh v&#7921;c c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; s&#7889; c&#361;ng gi&uacute;p c&aacute;c b&#7841;n tr&#7867; ph&aacute;t huy s&#7921; s&aacute;ng t&#7841;o, nghi&ecirc;n c&#7913;u, t&igrave;m t&ograve;i &#273;&#7875; t&#7841;o ra nh&#7919;ng gi&aacute; tr&#7883; h&#7919;u &iacute;ch cho x&atilde; h&#7897;i. M&#7897;t m&ocirc;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&ograve;i h&#7887;i ng&#432;&#7901;i tham gia ph&#7843;i kh&ocirc;ng ng&#7915;ng h&#7885;c h&#7887;i, r&egrave;n luy&#7879;n v&agrave; s&#7861;n s&agrave;ng &#273;&oacute;n nh&#7853;n nh&#7919;ng th&aacute;ch th&#7913;c. &#272;&acirc;y ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; tri&#7875;n v&#7885;ng v&agrave; c&#417; h&#7897;i &#273;&#7875; c&aacute;c b&#7841;n tr&#7867; &#273;&oacute;ng g&oacute;p gi&aacute; tr&#7883; c&#7911;a m&igrave;nh v&agrave;o s&#7921; ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n c&#7911;a &#273;&#7845;t n&#432;&#7899;c.</p><p style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 28.8px;\"><br></p></div></div>\n', 13, 37, '1717517132.jpeg', '2024-06-02 07:46:37', '2024-06-05 00:26:10');

